generated_code:
from typing import List, Optional, Dict, Set, Any
import heapq
import collections

class Solution:
    def findSecret(self, text: str) -> str:
        """
        Extracts the last word of the input string, which is the secret word.

        Args:
            text: The input string.

        Returns:
            The last word of the input string. If the input is empty, return an empty string.
        """
        if not text:
            return ""
        words = text.split()
        if not words:
            return ""
        return words[-1]
